OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1776874270
OL,3,CFraud of #39.5 million suspected in PM
OL,4,CLaw Group investigation
OL,6,FThe Solicitors Regulation Authority
OL,7,F(SRA) has confirmed that its
OL,8,Finvestigation into PM Law Group
OL,9,Fincludes suspected fraud of #39.5
OL,10,Fmillion.
OL,12,FThe SRA say that its investigation
OL,13,Finvolves a "sophisticated suspected
OL,14,Ffraud" and includes "improper removal
OL,15,Fand misuse of #39.5 million of client
OL,16,Ffunds."
OL,18,FButterworths Solicitors was one of the
OL,19,Fbrands of Sheffield-based PM Law Group
OL,20,Fand had four branches across Cumbria.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1776874270
OL,3,CFraud of #39.5 million suspected in PM
OL,4,CLaw Group investigation
OL,6,FThe SRA say that their intervention
OL,7,Finto PM Law Group is one of the
OL,8,Flargest and most complex ever taken.
OL,10,FThe regulator says that it is
OL,11,Fcontinuing to support thousands of
OL,12,Fformer clients who are impacted by the
OL,13,Ffirm's closure.
OL,15,FThe PM Law group was made up of 11
OL,16,Fcompanies, with 25 offices and more
OL,17,Fthan 30 trading names across
OL,18,FYorkshire, Cumbria, Berkshire,
OL,19,FDerbyshire and London.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1776874270
OL,3,CFraud of #39.5 million suspected in PM
OL,4,CLaw Group investigation
OL,6,FWhat support has the SRA given to
OL,7,Faffected clients so far?
OL,9,FPaul Hastings, SRA Director of Client
OL,10,FProtection said: "We are continuing to
OL,11,Fdo all we can to support former
OL,12,Fclients of PM Law, including by
OL,13,Freuniting them with their money or
OL,14,Ffiles.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1776874270
OL,3,CFraud of #39.5 million suspected in PM
OL,4,CLaw Group investigation
OL,6,F"Some of those affected were in the
OL,7,Fprocess of buying or selling a home,
OL,8,Ffacing the risk of collapsed moves, or
OL,9,Flosing their deposits. Others were
OL,10,Fdealing with delayed probate matters,
OL,11,Foften while managing bereavement and
OL,12,Foutstanding estate administration.
OL,14,F"Many of the former clients faced
OL,15,Fsignificant upheaval at a stressful
OL,16,Ftime, so we have been determined to
OL,17,Fprovide as much support as possible."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
